title: About Me
text: This is Jacob Vanderford’s Sports Data Blog. One of the nicknames I go by Vandy, hence the nickname for the title! I am a Sports Media & Communication and Advertising & Public Relations double major with Minors in Music and Theatre at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln. I’m passionate about sports, music and leadership, and the thing that engulfs them all: storytelling. Join me as I post some blogs that I write about various sports data sets and more!
